nodes.bodyText: Actually, what parameters do you want me to restore?
Hmm, somehow all the parameter names are lost... Like world, pos, etc
Ah yeah, I can fix that real quick.
Absolutely nothing! It’s called in world#setBlockState and PistonBlock#move, has no default impl, and no overrides.
That's a good point. I think we should name the field/arg materialColorFactory or colorFactory and have the method still be named materialColor
